        "title": "Human cytomegalovirus IE1 protein alters the higher-order chromatin structure by targeting the acidic patch of the nucleosome", 
        "published": "2016-01-26T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2016-01-26T00:00:00Z", 
